62
63class DisplayImpl : public EGLImplFactory, public angle::Subject
64{
65 public:
66 DisplayImpl(const egl::DisplayState &state);
67 ~DisplayImpl() override;
68
69 virtual egl::Error initialize(egl::Display *display) = 0;
70 virtual void terminate() = 0;
71 virtual egl::Error prepareForCall();
72 virtual egl::Error releaseThread();
73
74 virtual egl::Error makeCurrent(egl::Display *display,
75 egl::Surface *drawSurface,
76 egl::Surface *readSurface,
77 gl::Context *context) = 0;
78
79 virtual egl::ConfigSet generateConfigs() = 0;
80
81 virtual bool testDeviceLost() = 0;
82 virtual egl::Error restoreLostDevice(const egl::Display *display) = 0;
83
84 virtual bool isValidNativeWindow(EGLNativeWindowType window) const = 0;
85 virtual egl::Error validateClientBuffer(const egl::Config *configuration,
86 EGLenum buftype,
87 EGLClientBuffer clientBuffer,
88 const egl::AttributeMap &attribs) const;
89 virtual egl::Error validateImageClientBuffer(const gl::Context *context,
90 EGLenum target,
91 EGLClientBuffer clientBuffer,
92 const egl::AttributeMap &attribs) const;
93 virtual egl::Error validatePixmap(egl::Config *config,
94 EGLNativePixmapType pixmap,
95 const egl::AttributeMap &attributes) const;
96
97 virtual std::string getVendorString() const = 0;
98
99 virtual DeviceImpl *createDevice() = 0;
100
101 virtual egl::Error waitClient(const gl::Context *context) = 0;
102 virtual egl::Error waitNative(const gl::Context *context, EGLint engine) = 0;
103 virtual gl::Version getMaxSupportedESVersion() const = 0;
104 virtual gl::Version getMaxConformantESVersion() const = 0;
105 const egl::Caps &getCaps() const;
106
107 virtual void setBlobCacheFuncs(EGLSetBlobFuncANDROID set, EGLGetBlobFuncANDROID get) {}
108
109 const egl::DisplayExtensions &getExtensions() const;
110
111 void setBlobCache(egl::BlobCache *blobCache) { mBlobCache = blobCache; }
112 egl::BlobCache *getBlobCache() const { return mBlobCache; }
113
114 virtual void initializeFrontendFeatures(angle::FrontendFeatures *features) const {}
115
116 virtual void populateFeatureList(angle::FeatureList *features) = 0;
117
118 const egl::DisplayState &getState() const { return mState; }
119
120 virtual egl::Error handleGPUSwitch();
121
122 protected:
123 const egl::DisplayState &mState;
124
125 private:
126 virtual void generateExtensions(egl::DisplayExtensions *outExtensions) const = 0;
127 virtual void generateCaps(egl::Caps *outCaps) const = 0;
128
129 mutable bool mExtensionsInitialized;
130 mutable egl::DisplayExtensions mExtensions;
131
132 mutable bool mCapsInitialized;
133 mutable egl::Caps mCaps;
134
135 egl::BlobCache *mBlobCache;
136};
137
138} // namespace rx
